interferon response. At the same time efficient shRNA constructs allowed to partially
(IL6 shRNA-1) rescue the osteogenic differentiation from negative affect of TNFα, or
in case of IL6 shRNA-2 even to completely convert TNFα from inhibitor into a potentiator of osteogenesis.
